HEADWORD: nonrenewable
<hw>nonrenewable</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>That can not be renewed;
<as>as, a <ex>nonrenewable</ex> option; books on that shelf are
<ex>nonrenewable</ex></as>. Opposite of <ant>renewable</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> unrenewable.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

